---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Currency
permalink: /currency/
---
<p>Currency is the living layer of Openflows: what is currently moving through the system as conditions change. Three forms, each with a different level of stability and focus.</p>

<section class="currency-section">
  <div class="currency-section-header">
    <h2>Currents</h2>
    <span class="entry-count muted">{{ collections.currents.length }} entries</span>
  </div>
  <p class="meta">Provisional movement: signals, tensions, and early patterning from the open source AI ecosystem.</p>
  <ul class="currency-list">
    {% for item in collections.currents %}
      {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
        {% if item.data.abstract %}<p class="item-abstract">{{ item.data.abstract }}</p>{% endif %}
        <div class="item-meta">
          <span class="muted">{{ item.date | readableDate }}</span>
        </div>
      </li>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  <p><a href="/currency/currents/">View all currents →</a></p>
</section>

